title: The First Men In The Moon 2010 Dvdrip

sources.title: The First Men In The Moon 2010 Dvdrip
sources.description: In 1969, the Apollo moon landing is to be televised internationally but at a country fair in England a small boy named Jim meets the 90-year-old Julius Bedford who tells him that, in 1909, as a struggling writer, he met eccentric Professor Cavor, inventor of Cavorite, a gravity-defying substance which they used to build a sphere, which took them to the Moon.
